<p class=MsoNormal align="center"><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'><b>UltraViolet<sup>TM</sup> (Beta) Privacy 
Policy<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>The UltraViolet service and the
accompanying Web sites and user interfaces (collectively, <b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:
normal'>"UltraViolet"</b>) are provided by Digital Entertainment Content
Ecosystem (DECE) LLC and its affiliates (collectively, <b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:
normal'>"DECE"</b>). UltraViolet </span><span
lang=EN style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";mso-bidi-font-family:
"Times New Roman";mso-ansi-language:EN'>provides a </span><span
style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";mso-bidi-font-family:
"Times New Roman"'>digital rights locker solution which gives registered members
of an UltraViolet household <b
style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>"Household"</b>) one place to access to all
of the UltraViolet-compliant digital content (the <b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:
normal'>"Digital Content"</b>) purchased or rented by the Household. UltraViolet also provides registered users of
a Household account (each, a <b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>"Member"</b>)
the right to manage access to the Digital Content in the Household account, and
the right to register or update different UltraViolet-compliant devices for the
playback of the Digital Content (each, a <b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>"Device"</b>).</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";mso-bidi-font-family:
"Times New Roman"'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>This privacy policy (the <b
style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>"Privacy Policy"</b>) sets forth DECE's
information collection, use and disclosure practices with regard to
UltraViolet.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>By using UltraViolet, including
purchasing or renting Digital Content through UltraViolet, you are agreeing to
the terms of this Privacy Policy as they may be amended from time to time.In choosing to use UltraViolet, you therefore
are consenting to DECE's collection, use and disclosure of your Personal
Information (as defined below) and UltraViolet Usage Information (including
information about what Digital Content you purchase, rent or otherwise access
through the Household account) as described in this Privacy Policy.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>As UltraViolet is updated and expanded,
this Privacy Policy may change, so please check back to review this page from
time to time. This Privacy Policy is
incorporated into, and part of, <span style='mso-bidi-font-weight:bold'>the </span>
<a href= http://www.uvvu.com/Consent/Text/urn:dece:policy:coordinator:EndUserLicenseAgreement/html/Current>UltraViolet Beta Terms of Use </a>, which governs your use of
UltraViolet in general.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

