style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";mso-bidi-font-family:
"Times New Roman"'>You may opt in or opt out of DECE's sharing of your Personal
Information with third parties for marketing purposes by following the
directions in the "Right to Opt In and Opt Out" [Embed hyperlink] section
below.</i></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>UltraViolet is intended for Members who
are located in the United States of America.This Privacy Policy shall be interpreted under the laws of the United
States.</span><b><i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:
