<p class=MsoNormal><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span
style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";mso-bidi-font-family:
"Times New Roman"'><a name="purpose">Purpose and Scope of this Policy</a><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Protecting the privacy of Personal
Information is very important to DECE. This Privacy Policy explains, in general, what Personal Information and
other information is collected through UltraViolet, how the information is
used, and with whom DECE may share such information. <b>"Personal Information"</b> means
information that may identify Members as individuals or allow online or offline
contact with Members as individuals, including, for example, your name; display
name; username; physical address; e-mail address; telephone number; photo or
chosen image; age; date of birth, security questions and answers; parental
controls; individual demographic information; Digital Content purchase or
rental information, including, without limitation, title, artist, date of
purchase, and place of purchase; information regarding your Digital Content
streams and usage; the number of, and the makes and models of, the Devices you
have added to the Household account; and the number of Members registered to
the Household account and their Personal Information.<o:p></o:p></span></p>


<p class=MsoNormal><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span
style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";mso-bidi-font-family:
"Times New Roman"'><a name="right">Right to Opt In and Opt Out</a></span></b><span
style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";mso-bidi-font-family:
"Times New Roman"'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>You may have the right to "opt in" to
certain of DECE's uses and disclosures of your Personal Information. For example, at the time you create the Household,
and anytime thereafter by accessing the Household account, or through the Web
site of a retailer providing UltraViolet-compliant Digital Content (a <b
style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>"Retailer"</b>), you may have the
opportunity to opt in to (1) allowing Retailers to access and display to you
the Digital Content associated with the Household (including Digital Content
that you obtained from another Retailer), (2) allowing Retailers to market to
you based on the contents of the Household account, (3) receiving promotional
offers from DECE, and (4) receiving third-party offers.Once you opt-in, you will then have the right
to change your mind and opt-out.<b
style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'></b><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Please understand that, even if you
opt-out of receiving promotional correspondence from DECE, DECE and its
authorized service providers may still contact you in connection with your
relationship, activities, transactions and communications with DECE and the Household
account. Also, if you wish to stop receiving
promotional messages from third parties with whom DECE has already shared your
contact information, you will need to contact them directly.<b
style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'> <o:p></o:p></b></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-outline-level:1'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:
normal'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'><a name="what">What Information is Collected through UltraViolet?</a><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>In order to make the most of your use
of UltraViolet, DECE collects Personal Information about you, from you, your
computer, and registered Devices.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman";mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:
EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA'><br clear=all style='page-break-before:always'>
</span></b>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:.5in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:
normal'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Member-Provided Information</span></b><span
style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";mso-bidi-font-family:
"Times New Roman"'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>DECE collects Personal Information from
Members of UltraViolet, for example, through Members' submission of
registration information when they open new Households or add Members to
existing Households, modify information in the Household accounts, request and
receive customer service, and otherwise in the course of their use of
UltraViolet. Such information is also
collected, for example, when a Member subscribes for features through
UltraViolet, makes purchases of or rents Digital Content, completes surveys,
submits a comment or question to DECE using a "contact us" or similar feature
on the Web Site, sends DECE an e-mail, or in any other way submits Personal
Information to DECE. <b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><o:p></o:p></b></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>You may be able to send information
about UltraViolet to your friends and family members.In some of these cases, you may provide the
e-mail address of your friend or family member to DECE.Such information will be treated in
accordance with this Privacy Policy and applicable law. <b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:
normal'><o:p></o:p></b></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:.5in;page-break-after:avoid'><b
style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:
"Arial","sans-serif";mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Information
Automatically Collected ("UltraViolet Usage Information") </span></b><span
style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";mso-bidi-font-family:
"Times New Roman"'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:.5in;page-break-after:avoid'><b
style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:
"Arial","sans-serif";mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Cookies</span></b><span
style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";mso-bidi-font-family:
"Times New Roman"'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>DECE may use "cookies" to keep, and
sometimes track, information about you.Cookies are small data files that are sent to your browser or related
software from a Web server and stored on your computer or Device. Cookies track your activities and preferences
while using UltraViolet.<b> </b>They
may, for example, store your username and/or password. A cookie may enable DECE to relate your use
of UltraViolet to other information about you, including your Personal
Information. All of these purposes serve
to improve and personalize your experience using UltraViolet, including this
Site. <b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'> <span style='mso-bidi-font-weight:bold'><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Most Web browsers can be set to inform
you when a cookie has been sent to you and provide you with the opportunity to
refuse that cookie. Additionally, if you
have a Flash player installed on your computer, your Flash player can be set to
reject or delete Flash cookies.<b> </b>However,
refusing a cookie may, in some cases, preclude you from using, or negatively
impact the display or function of, UltraViolet or certain areas or features of
UltraViolet. <b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:
normal'>By using UltraViolet, you consent to DECE's use of cookies as described
above.</b> <o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:.5in'><b><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Clear
GIFs<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>


<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>DECE may use "clear GIFs" (aka "Web
beacons" or "pixel tags") or similar technologies to enable DECE to know
whether you have visited a Web page, viewed content, or received a
message. A clear GIF is typically a one-pixel,
transparent image (although it can be a visible image as well), located on a
Web page or in an e-mail or other type of content or message, which is
retrieved from a remote site on the Internet enabling the verification of an
individual's viewing or receipt of a Web page, content or message. A clear GIF may enable DECE to relate your
viewing or receipt of a Web page, content or message to other information about
you, including your Personal Information.<b><o:p></o:p></b></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:.5in;mso-outline-level:1'><b
style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:
"Arial","sans-serif";mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>IP Address,
Clickstream Data, and Device Information<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>DECE's servers automatically collect
data about your Internet address when you use UltraViolet. This information, known as an Internet
Protocol address, or IP Address, is a number that's automatically assigned to
your computer or Device by your Internet service provider or carrier whenever
you're online. DECE's servers may also
record the Web page from which you linked to the Web Site (e.g., another Web
site or a search engine); the pages you visit on the Web Site; the Web site you
visit after the Web Site; the ads you see and/or click on; other information
about the type of Web browser, computer, Device, platform, related software and
settings you are using; any search terms you have entered on the Web Site or a
referral site; and other usage activity and data logged by DECE's servers. DECE uses this information for internal
system administration, to help diagnose problems with DECE's servers, and to
administer UltraViolet. Such information
may also be used to gather broad demographic information, such as country of origin
and Internet service provider or carrier. DECE may also link this information with your Personal Information. <b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><o:p></o:p></b></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Any or all of these activities with
regard to UltraViolet Usage Information may be performed on DECE's behalf by
DECE's services providers.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span
style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";mso-bidi-font-family:
"Times New Roman"'><a name="privacy">Privacy of Children</a><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>UltraViolet is not directed to persons <span
class=GramE>under</span> 18 years of age at this time. The UltraViolet <span class=GramE>services are</span> not currently designed to attract those
under the age of 18 and we do not intentionally collect personal information
from children on our site. <o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='page-break-after:avoid'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:
normal'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'><a name="#how">How is the Personal Information and
UltraViolet Usage Information used?</a><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='page-break-after:avoid'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>DECE
will use the Personal Information you provide through UltraViolet, and
UltraViolet Usage Information, for example, to provide you with UltraViolet
services, products and information, customer service, and otherwise to respond
to your requests. DECE may also use your
Personal Information and UltraViolet Usage Information to maintain DECE's
internal recordkeeping. DECE may match
information collected from you through different means or at different times,
including both Personal Information and UltraViolet Usage Information, and use
such information along with information obtained from other sources, including
third parties. <o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>In addition, DECE may send you notices
(for example, in the form of e-mails, mailings, and the like), and otherwise
correspond with you, about products, services, companies and events, sponsored
by DECE and others, that DECE think might interest you. You may opt out of
receiving such notices from DECE by </span><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
font-family:"Arial","sans-serif"'>visiting the "Profile" area of the Household
account.</span><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'> <b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><o:p></o:p></b></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>DECE may analyze user behavior as a
measure of interest in, and use of, UltraViolet, both on an individual basis
and in the aggregate.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-outline-level:1'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:
normal'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'><a name="does">Does DECE share Personal Information
or UltraViolet Usage Information with others?</a><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:.5in'><b><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman";
layout-grid-mode:line'>Other Members <span class=GramE>Of</span> The Household <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman";layout-grid-mode:line;mso-bidi-font-weight:
bold'>Other Members of the Household may have access to the information
contained in the Household account.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:.5in'><b><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman";
layout-grid-mode:line'>UltraViolet Partners<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman";layout-grid-mode:line;mso-bidi-font-weight:
bold'>DECE works with partners to provide UltraViolet. These partners include the publishers that
create the Digital Content that is UltraViolet-compatible, the Retailers that
sell or rent such Digital Content to UltraViolet Members, the service providers
that host and/or stream the Digital Content for your use, the makers of the
Devices that you use to access Digital Content through UltraViolet, and the
service providers that implement and maintain UltraViolet (collectively, &quot;<b>UltraViolet
Partners</b>&quot;). In order to provide
you with the UltraViolet service and its various features, DECE shares your
Personal Information and UltraViolet Usage Information with UltraViolet
Partners. For example, DECE shares such
information with Retailers so that Retailers can check whether you already have
Digital Content in the Household that you are intending to purchase or rent
again, make recommendations of Digital Content you may be interested in, and to
enable you to add Devices to the Household through Retailers' Web sites.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:.5in'><b><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'><a name="service">Service Providers</a><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>DECE may use third-party service
providers to help operate UltraViolet and deliver UltraViolet products,
services or information, and may share your information with such service
providers (such as Web site or customer service providers, database hosting
companies, address list hosting companies, e-mail service providers, analytics
companies, distribution companies, fulfillment companies, and other similar
service providers that use such information on DECE's behalf). <o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:.5in'><b><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman";
layout-grid-mode:line'>Public Forums<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman";layout-grid-mode:line'>When you
contribute to a public area or feature of UltraViolet, such as a chat room,
bulletin board, list serve,</span><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:
"Arial","sans-serif";mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'> blog, wiki or
other communication or community tool or area, the information that you submit
or post will be made available to the general public, including other uses of
UltraViolet. For this reason, DECE recommends
that you do not submit any sensitive information, including your full name,
home address, phone number, other information that would enable other users to
locate you, or financial information on these areas of the Web Site. Instead, make up a username that does not
disclose your personal identity. <b
style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span
style='layout-grid-mode:line'><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>


<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:.5in;page-break-after:avoid'><b
style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:
"Arial","sans-serif";mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'><a name="legal">Legal Disclosures</a><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>DECE may disclose information to
government authorities, and to other third parties when compelled to do so by
government authorities, at DECE's discretion, or otherwise as required or
permitted by law, including but not limited to in response to court orders and
subpoenas. DECE also may disclose
information when DECE has reason to believe that someone is causing injury to
or interference with DECE's rights or property, other users of UltraViolet, or
anyone else that could be harmed by such activities. <b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:
normal'><o:p></o:p></b></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:.5in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:
normal'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Business Transfer<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>In the event that DECE or substantially
all of its assets relating to UltraViolet are acquired by one or more third
parties as a result of an acquisition, merger, sale, reorganization,
consolidation or liquidation, Personal Information and UltraViolet Usage
Information may be among the transferred assets.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<h1><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";mso-bidi-font-family:
"Times New Roman"'><a name="your">Your Access Rights</a><br
style='mso-special-character:line-break'>
<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>
<![endif]><o:p></o:p></span></h1>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-outline-level:1'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>You
may review, update or modify the Personal Information that is stored in your Member
profile on the UltraViolet Web Site by visiting the "Profile" area of the Household
account.<b></b><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:
normal'><o:p></o:p></b></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span
style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";mso-bidi-font-family:
"Times New Roman"'><a name="security">Security</a><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>
<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>
<![endif]></span></b><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>While DECE endeavors to protect the
security and integrity of sensitive Personal Information collected via
UltraViolet, due to the inherent nature of the Internet as an open global
communications vehicle, DECE cannot guarantee that any information, during
transmission through the Internet or while stored on DECE's system or otherwise
in DECE's care, will be absolutely safe from intrusion by others, such as
hackers.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>If you contact DECE by e-mail or a
"contact us" or similar feature on DECE's Web Site, you should be aware that
your transmission might not be secure while it is transmitted over the
Internet. A third party could view
information you send by these methods in transit. <o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoBodyText3><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Once you establish a Household, you
will be responsible for any access to or use of the Household account by you or
any person or entity using your password, whether or not such access or use has
been authorized by or on behalf of you, and whether or not such person or
entity is your employee or agent. You
should, therefore, take all necessary precautions to ensure the confidentiality
of your password. Please notify DECE of
any unauthorized use of your password or the Household account or any other
breach of security relating to your Personal Information, this Site, or
UltraViolet more generally.<b
style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><o:p></o:p></b></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>In the unlikely event that DECE
believes that the security of your Personal Information in DECE's possession or
control may have been compromised, DECE may seek to notify you of that
development. If a notification is
appropriate, DECE would endeavor to do so as promptly as possible under the
circumstances, and, to the extent DECE has your e-mail address, DECE may notify
you by e-mail. Absent your written
instruction to the contrary, by using UltraViolet, you are <b>consenting to
DECE's use of e-mail as a means of such notification.</b> <b>If you wish to withhold such consent and
request that DECE use the United States Postal Service to notify you in this
situation, please e-mail DECE at</b> <b><a href="mailto:html.admin@decellc.com">admin@decellc.com</a>. </b><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-outline-level:1'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:
normal'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'><a name="consent">Consent to Processing</a><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>By providing Personal Information to
DECE, you consent to the collection, maintenance, processing and transfer of
such information in and to the United States and other countries and
territories, pursuant to the laws of the United States, which may provide
lesser privacy protections than the laws of other countries. <b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><i
style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'><o:p></o:p></i></b></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-outline-level:1'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:
normal'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'><a name="linked">"Linked-To" Web Sites</a></span></b><span
style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";mso-bidi-font-family:
"Times New Roman"'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";
mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>When you are using UltraViolet, you may
have the opportunity to visit, or link to, other Web sites, including other Web
sites operated by unaffiliated third parties.These sites may collect Personal Information about you. 
DECE does not control sites that are operated
by these entities and is not responsible for the information practices of these
sites. This Privacy Policy does not
address the information practices of other Web sites.<o:p></o:p></span></p>



