posting to this Web Site.&nbsp; Whenever we amend the Privacy Policy, we will
revise the "Effective Date" at the bottom of this page.Continued use of <span class=GramE>UltraViolet</span>
following any changes shall indicate your acknowledgement of and consent to such
changes. Under certain circumstances
(for example, in connection with certain material changes), DECE may also elect
to notify you of changes or updates to this Privacy Policy, or to request your
consent for such changes, by additional means, such as posting a notice on the
front page of the Web Site or sending you an e-mail. <b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:
